click is a 2006 american fantasy comedy film directed by frank coraci , written by steve koren and mark o'keefe , and produced by adam sandler , who also starred in the lead role . the film co-stars kate beckinsale as his wife donna and christopher walken as morty . sandler plays an overworked architect who neglects his family . when he acquires a universal remote that enables him to " fast forward " through unpleasant or outright dull parts of his life , he soon learns that those seemingly bad moments that he skips over contained valuable time with his family and important life lessons . throughout the story , a man named morty explains how the remote works and issues warnings . filming began in late 2005 and was finished by early 2006 . the film was released in the united states on june 23 , 2006 , by columbia pictures . it was nominated for an academy award for best makeup , making this the only sandler film to be nominated for an oscar .